name: Cube Race (Finding Nobody)
description:
To begin you have to open the file double click on Cube_Race_Main and when that opens up hit the arrow button in the top left. Cube Race is a game where you race to a finish line against a friend. There are seven levels, but a random five will play. It is a good example of a processing game. 

Music by C4T:  soundcloud.com/c4t_noah
